title: Wutanfall (DDR Punk) (1981-84) (MP3 320k)
description:
This CD came with the book  "Wutanfall. Punk in der DDR 1982 bis 1989. Die Protagonisten damals und heute" published in 2017. It contains eight songs, recorded in the period 1981-1984 in Leipzig, East-Germany by the punk band Wutanfall ("Rage" or "Tantrum").

Chaos (Jürgen Gutjahr) - vocals (until 1983)
Stracke (Bernd "Pepsie" Stracke) - vocals (started 1983)
Typhus (Andreas Schmits) - guitar
Imad (Imad Abdul-Majid) - guitar, vocals (until 1983)
Zappa (Frank Zappe) - bass
Rotz (Uwe Plociennik) - drums

01 Messestadtpunk
02 Leipzig in Trümmern
03 Stürze den Papst
04 Dracula
05 Frankenstein
06 Du kotzt mich an
07 Kinderlied
08 Vorsicht
